<br>
I think you'll be fine if you are comming to fish. You might prefer to fish a little farther from Mountian Home. Generally the Norfork is the favorite after meeting place to fish. If you ran into pressure you could fish the Bull Shoal Dam or Wildcat Shoal and you might not see another person.<br>
